{"id":146,"date":"2017-02-11T09:56:37","date_gmt":"2017-02-11T09:56:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=146"},"modified":"2020-08-31T11:53:30","modified_gmt":"2020-08-31T11:53:30","slug":"setup-cron-job","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/setup-cron-job\/","title":{"rendered":"Setup cPanel Cron Job"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">Cron is required to be set up for Perfex CRM if you want all features to works as expected.<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Setup cPanel Cron Job<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Login to your cPanel and navigate to <b>Cron jobs<\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Add the following settings :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"864\" height=\"295\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1.png\" alt=\"Setup cPanel Cron Job\" class=\"wp-image-147\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1.png 864w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1-300x102.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1-768x262.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1-60x20.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/setup-cron-job-1-150x51.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><code>wget -q -O- http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/crm\/cron\/index<\/code><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><b>Change the URL according to your base URL<\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Eq.&nbsp;if it&#8217;s on root domain you need to type only http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/cron\/index<\/li><li>Eq. on subfolder \/crm you will need to type http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/crm\/cron\/index<\/li><li>If your <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/faq\/what-is-base-url\/\">base URL<\/a> starts with <strong>https:\/\/<\/strong>, make sure that you configure the cron job URL to start with <strong>https:\/\/<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert-info \">This is CRON Job URL and not a path. Your server&nbsp;needs to support wget command to call the wget command and execute. <strong>You can find your Perfex CRM installation cron job url located at Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Cron Job<\/strong><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"plesk\">Setup Plesk Cron Job<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Refer to cPanel cron job examples to get your cron URL.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For Plesk use one of the following configurations:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"807\" height=\"578\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1204\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1.png 807w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1-768x550.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1-60x43.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk1-150x107.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 807px) 100vw, 807px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>If the first example is not working for you try this config:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"831\" height=\"541\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1205\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2.png 831w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2-300x195.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2-768x500.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2-60x39.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/plesk2-150x98.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 831px) 100vw, 831px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Common issues<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>My server does not support wget command?<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If your server does not support wget command you try one of the following commands:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted lang:default decode:true\">php \/home\/username\/public_html\/installation_folder\/index.php cron\/index &gt;&gt; \/dev\/null<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted lang:default decode:true\">php \/home\/username\/public_html\/installation_folder\/index.php cron\/index<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>If that doesn\u2019t work, it probably means you don\u2019t have the package php5-cli installed. On <strong>debian \/ ubuntu<\/strong> you can install this package as follows:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted lang:default decode:true\">sudo apt-get install php5-cli<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are not able to install packages, you can specify your path to php try the following command:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted lang:default decode:true\">\/usr\/local\/bin\/php -f \/home\/username\/public_html\/installation_folder\/index.php cron index<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Replace <strong>username<\/strong> and <strong>installation_folder<\/strong> to fit your path.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If none of the commands are not working, you can use some free cron job service like&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.easycron.com\">https:\/\/www.easycron.com<\/a>. Mostly the free cron job services have a limit to execute every 20 minutes but it will work well too with Perfex CRM.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Testing the cron job<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to test if your cron job config works fine after you configure it, you can create custom <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/faq\/what-is-the-reminders-feature-inside-perfex-crm\/\">staff reminder.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From the main menu click<strong>&nbsp;Customers -&gt; [Customer] -&gt; Reminders<\/strong>&nbsp;tab and <strong>create a reminder for your user with the nearest date<\/strong> eq if your time is 09:50 add reminder for 09:51. Wait 5 minutes the cron job to run to notify you, you should receive a notification inside the CRM, the notification should be visible on the top right side bell.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you received the notification, then this means that the cron job config is properly configured.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Setup cPanel Cron Job Login to your cPanel and navigate to Cron jobs Add the following settings : wget -q -O- http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/crm\/cron\/index Change the URL according to your base URL Eq.&nbsp;if it&#8217;s on root domain you need to type only http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/cron\/index Eq. on subfolder \/crm you will need to type http:\/\/yourdomain.com\/crm\/cron\/index If your base URL [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[31],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-146","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-setup-and-configuration"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/146","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=146"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/146\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"hr